import React from 'react';
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import '../../styles/output.css';

function MenuBar() {
	return (

		<section
			className="
				fixed
				top-0 right-0
				h-2/4 w-2/5
				z-30
				bg-white
				shadow-2xl
				pt-16
				rounded-md
			"
		>
			<nav
				className="
					flex flex-col items-center 
				"
			>
				<NavLink 
					exact to="/" 
					className="
						w-full
						p-6 
						focus:bg-primary
						text-center
						text
					" 
					activeStyle = {{
						backgroundColor: "#D49b7a"
					}}
				>Início</NavLink>
				<NavLink 
					to="/servicos" 
					className="
						w-full
						p-6 
						focus:bg-primary
						text-center
					"
					activeStyle = {{
						backgroundColor: "#D49b7a"
					}}
				>Serviços</NavLink>
				<NavLink 
					to="/contato" 
					className="
						w-full
						p-6 
						focus:bg-primary
						text-center
					"
					activeStyle = {{
						backgroundColor: "#D49b7a"
					}}
				>Contato</NavLink>
				<NavLink 
					to="/sobre" 
					className="
						w-full
						p-6	
						focus:bg-primary
						text-center				
					"
					activeStyle = {{
						backgroundColor: "#D49b7a"
					}}
				>Sobre</NavLink>
			</nav>

		</section>


	);
}

export default MenuBar;
